33:23.580 --> 33:25.880
♪ How our hearts
are doing now ♪

33:25.880 --> 33:27.540
(sobbing)

33:27.540 --> 33:32.380
♪ God knows the both
of us have tried ♪

33:32.380 --> 33:35.080
♪ We were so in love,
