- Hey.
- Thanks.

33:59.000 --> 34:00.040
- Hi.

34:03.080 --> 34:04.710
- I just wanted to help.

34:04.710 --> 34:06.880
- Of course.
Come on back.

34:11.580 --> 34:13.120
- What does it mean
to be making this album

34:13.120 --> 34:16.080
with Deacon about
your life together?

34:16.080 --> 34:17.830
- It means everything.

34:19.710 --> 34:21.500
I could bore you with
all the details

34:21.500 --> 34:23.420
of what brought us
to this moment.

34:23.420 --> 34:26.750
But let me just tell you that
this album and being able

34:26.750 --> 34:30.790
to be married to him and
have him be the father

34:30.790 --> 34:36.670
of my children, finally
after all these years,

34:36.670 --> 34:39.040
we've got a lot
of water under the bridge.

34:39.040 --> 34:42.000
