and I've seen Deacon

34:42.000 --> 34:43.790
go through all of it

34:43.790 --> 34:47.620
and he always comes up
stronger than he was before.

34:47.620 --> 34:50.000
He's just incredible that way.

34:50.000 --> 34:53.000
He never gives up.

34:53.000 --> 34:57.000
