strength in my life every day?

34:57.000 --> 35:01.620
And to see him being
that way with our children?

35:01.620 --> 35:06.210
And to know that
he's the best father

35:06.210 --> 35:07.880
that they could ever ask for?

35:09.710 --> 35:14.420
And the best part
about is that I know

35:14.420 --> 35:16.670
he's never gonna
give up on me

35:16.670 --> 35:19.170
or on my girls.

35:21.080 --> 35:24.080
Or on our record

35:24.080 --> 35:26.460
or in any other damn thing
I drag him into.

35:26.460 --> 35:29.620
(laughs)

35:29.620 --> 35:33.460
He's gonna be there.

35:33.460 --> 35:35.120
Pretty lucky.

